<div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-block">
  <a class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="/rnode/<%= host %>/<%= port %>/?token=<%= password %>">
    Launch Selkies Desktop
  </a>
</div>

<p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
  Selkies is listening on <code><%= host %>:<%= port %></code> through the OnDemand node proxy.
</p>

<p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-0">
  The launch link includes a per-session Selkies token generated by Open OnDemand.
</p>
